paragraph.text:
the term grandchild, used with
				respect to an employee, means any person who is a son or daughter of a son or
				daughter of the employee;

the term
				grandparent, used with respect to an employee, means a parent of a
				parent of the employee;

the term
				parent-in-law, used with respect to an employee, means a parent of
				the spouse or domestic partner of the employee;
